However, the deviation, unlike the bees, can not occur up, down, or even diagonally - it can only be two-dimensional, and only in the direction of the reversibility of the tyres.
While the bees here are infinitely open many ways to depart from other bees, the researchers were able to use only the rotary movement, the relative acceleration and braking at the author.
The BR23C contains lithium polymer batteries, which are lighter and more energy-efficient, and therefore have a longer lifetime than conventional lithium-ion batteries.
Andoh explained that it concerns the instinctive, intelligent response, and less on data processing, and even less on the ability to store them.
This device only needs to process a few inputs per second and respond to them accordingly.
It doesn’t have to save them, or produce an intuitive, logical reaction using previous manipulations, so it’s constantly only a handful of KB Memory.
There is no Gigabyte and Megabyte hard memory.
This is the first step in developing the immediate collision prevention technology that Nissan estimates will be in production in the next 10 years.
Another application could find the technology in GPS satellite navigation by consciously directing the driver around obstacles and leading it to the target.
